      <title>波斯尼亚随着塞族分裂演讲的忧虑而攀升欧盟议程</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/bosnia-climbs-up-eu-agenda-as-serb-secession-talk-stokes-worry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波斯尼亚 - 黑塞哥维那在欧盟峰会上被添加到议程中，因为领导人的警报持续了警告，该领导人的潜在瓦解巴尔干国家可能会释放东南欧的动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/bosnia-climbs-up-eu-agenda-as-serb-secession-talk-stokes-worry</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 16:14:59 GMT</pubDate>
